## PHASE 3 — ARCHIVE INSTEAD OF DELETE

This is the critical change from any previous prompt version.
**Do NOT delete state files. Archive them.**

### 3.1  Find the existing cleanup block

If the script has an existing block that cleans up state files
at session start (found in Phase 1), it likely looks like:

```bash
